@startuml
actor User
actor Admin

participant System
participant Sensor
participant Payment

User -> System: Check availability
System -> Sensor: Get parking data
Sensor --> System: Availability
System --> User: Show spaces

User -> System: Reserve spot
System --> User: Confirm reservation

User -> System: Pay fee
System -> Payment: Process payment
Payment --> System: Success
System --> User: Payment confirmed

Admin -> System: View occupancy
System --> Admin: Show data
@enduml